description:
Jared is currently working on his master's degree in economics.
"I'd like to get my PhD," he explained. "It's going to take some time, but I'm enjoying it."
"What would you like to do when you get out?"
"I don't know," he said. "I'd like to focus on econometrics."
I have no idea what that is, so I didn't ask!
"The economy is kind of up in the air right now," he said. "Maybe by the time I graduate it will have sorted itself out."
Jared isn't all business, though. He likes to play baseball, hockey, and golf, and he loves to go to clubs to meet new people.
"I'm from the upper midwest," he said. "In the winter it's extremely cold so there isn't much else to do!"
When I first met Jared, I thought he was a bit on the nerdy side. Once he took his clothes off, I couldn't believe it!
"That's the quite the body you're hiding there," I said.
"That's what people tell me," he said modestly.
He really does have a great body! Totally ripped and a 100% perfect ass!
title: Jared
